title: Rollins, Richards among attendees at jazz foundation benefit
text: Rollins, Richards among attendees at jazz foundation benefit Tuesday, 20 October 2015 (7 minutes ago) Saxophonist Sonny Rollins will receive a lifetime achievement prize from the Jazz Foundation of America, and Keith Richards will be on hand at the gala to honor former Rolling Stones backup singer Merry Clayton.
